{{DISPLAYTITLE:''Kuroko's Basketball'' discography}} {{Infobox artist discography | Artist = ''[[Kuroko's Basketball]]'' | Image = | Caption = | EP = 1 | Singles = 27 | Soundtrack = 1 | References = Yes | Ref link = References }}
A number of musical CDs have been created for the media franchise built around Tadatoshi Fujimaki's [[manga]] ''[[Kuroko's Basketball]]''. Various theme songs and [[character song]]s were released on a total of 27 singles. One [[extended play]] and one [[soundtrack]] have also been released.
The anime television series currently consists of four pieces of theme music; two opening themes and two ending themes.
