mi-high-rise/|title=Tutor to Build Miami High-Rise|author=Golan, Elliot|date=June 12, 2014|work=San Fernando Valley Business Journal|accessdate=August 14, 2014}}</ref> * [[Paramount Bay at Edgewater Square]] – a high-rise condominium building in the Edgewater Neighborhood * [[Riverfront (Miami)|Riverfront]] – complex containing three main towers: "Mint" and "The Ivy" and "Wind" * [[Ten Museum Park]] – residential skyscraper * [[Toscano (Miami)|Toscano]] – group of residential condos in the Dadeland neighborhood * [[Villa Magna Condominiums]] – urban development that was planned to rise in Brickell; the [[Great Recession in the United States|housing crisis of the late 2000s]] halted the project
